<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><h1><a href="#spring-batch-2-1-9-release-is-available-download-github-a-href-http-bit-ly-nyxitl-http-bit-ly-nyxitl-a-or-maven-central-thanks-to-all-contributors" class="anchor" name="spring-batch-2-1-9-release-is-available-download-github-a-href-http-bit-ly-nyxitl-http-bit-ly-nyxitl-a-or-maven-central-thanks-to-all-contributors"></a>spring #batch 2.1.9.RELEASE is available (download github <a href="https://bit.ly/NYXItL">http://bit.ly/NYXItL</a> or Maven central). Thanks to all contributors!</h1>
<p>It’s mostly bugfixes for 2.1.8, plus a few interesting additions (e.g. nested tasklets from any namespace to support Spring Hadoop): <a href="http://static.springsource.org/sprin...1.8-2.1.9.html">http://static.springsource.org/sprin...1.8-2.1.9.html</a>.</p>
<p>The first real commit for 2.2 came in as a pull request. Nice work! Please keep them coming.</p>
</div>
